text: Katharine Charlotte Deirdre Brownlow (born 16 August 1964) is a British rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:British female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Altrincham
